= Ethics committee <app_ethics>

== PPMI dataset

This thesis was conducted in accordance with the guidelines established in the
#link("https://www.ppmi-info.org/sites/default/files/docs/PPMI%20Data%20User%20Guide.pdf",
"PPMI Data Use and Publication Policies"). The PPMI study itself received
approval from the relevant ethics committees, and all participants provided
informed consent prior to enrollment.

Data were stored exclusively on password-protected VICOROB servers.

== LLM use

Usage of Large Language Models (LLMs) was limited to proofreading, language
revisions, and assistance with isolated coding tasks. That being said, all
content in this thesis and in the final code submitted to the repository has
been read and validated. The design decisions regarding CNN architectures,
algorithms, experimental procedures and methodologies are either my
own or inspired by scientific documentation.
